==English==
===Noun===
'''salvation'''
# (''religion'') the process of being saved, the state of having been saved (from hell)
# Plan of salvation: 1. Believe that you are a sinner worthy of hell. 2. Believe that you can do nothing to get yourself out of hell. 3. Believe that Jesus Christ died for your sins so that you would not have to. 4. Believe that He will save you today if you ask Him to.

